title: Glee: The Ultimate Fifth Season, Part One
description:
The first part of Glee's fifth season, with the first 13 episodes.

1. Love Love Love [1]
2. Tina in the Sky with Diamonds [2]
3. The Quarterback
4. A Katy or a Gaga
5. The End of Twerk
6. Movin' Out
7. Puppet Master
8. Previously Unaired Christmas
9. Frenemies
10. Trio
11. City of Angels
12. 100 [1]
13. New Directions [2]

This package also includes the music released through these 13 episodes.

As an added bonus, in separate episode folders, I have included the original versions of the songs featured on Glee. This is something I do myself.
